<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>UI Shows bad request error and stay on the same screen</p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">500 (Unexpected Error)</span></p></td=
>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<br></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
A server error in the EXP API layer or downstream returns 500 errors.</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
EXP API returns 500 with message&nbsp;<br>
 "Something went wrong. Please <span style=3D"text-decoration: underline;">=
try again</span><span>."</span></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>UI Shows server error screen</p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td rowspan=3D"3" class=3D"confluenceTd">Beneficiary Management Enterprise =
INF API</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">400 (Input validation)</span></p></td=
>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><br></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>INF API beneficiary IDs validation raises exc=
eption if:</p>
<ul>
<li>Required fields are missing in the request.</li>
<li>Empty object is passed to the downstream</li>
<li>Request data is not in expected data format&nbsp;</li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">INF API returns 400</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
UI Shows bad request error and stay on the same screen</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">40=
4 (Input validation)</span></span></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><br></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>INF API beneficiary IDs validation raises exc=
eption if:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Requested ID cannot be found.</li>
<li>The record to be updated/archived is already in ARCHIVED state.&nbsp;</=
li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">INF API returns 404</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
UI Shows bad request error and stay on the same screen</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">500 (Unexpected Error)</span></p></td=
>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">A server error in the INF API server or the erro=
r updating data to the data store</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">INF API returns 500</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
UI Shows server error screen</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p><br></p>
